\fs36 \cf0 \cb2 \outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 Regen Studio took the lead in creating a groundbreaking position paper on Trusted Digital Product Passports (tDPPs) for {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://fides.community/"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 \strokec4 FIDES}}, partly commissioned by the Dutch Blockchain Coalition. \cb1 \

